<varlistentry id="options.SloppyFocus">
	<term>SloppyFocus</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Specifies  that  windows  retain  focus until the mouse moves to
		another window, or Warping causes another window to gain  focus.</para>
		<para>SloppyFocus has no effect if ClickToFocus is also specified.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
